sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Operator User
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Delink as Delink Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Queue as RabbitMQ
    participant Bank as Bank API
    participant SMS as SMS Gateway

    Note over User,SMS: Delink Workflow Sequence

    User->>API: POST /delink<br/>MSISDN, NIN, BVN
    API->>Auth: Validate JWT Token
    Auth->>Auth: Verify permissions
    Auth-->>API: OK
    API->>Delink: Create delink request
    Delink->>DB: Insert request<br/>(status: submitted)
    DB-->>Delink: Request ID
    Delink->>Queue: Publish<br/>delink.request.created
    Queue-->>Delink: ACK
    Delink-->>API: Request ID + status
    API-->>User: 201 Created

    Queue->>Bank: Process delink event
    Bank->>Bank: Validate linkage
    alt Bank Approves
        Bank->>DB: Update status<br/>bank_approved
        DB-->>Bank: OK
        Bank->>Queue: Publish<br/>delink.bank.approved
    else Bank Rejects
        Bank->>DB: Update status<br/>bank_rejected
        DB-->>Bank: OK
        Bank->>Queue: Publish<br/>delink.bank.rejected
    end

    Queue->>Delink: Consume approval event
    Delink->>DB: Fetch request details
    DB-->>Delink: Request data
    Delink->>DB: Update status<br/>delink_in_progress
    DB-->>Delink: OK
    Delink->>Bank: Execute delink<br/>(update records)
    Bank-->>Delink: Delink confirmed

    alt Delink Success
        Delink->>DB: Update status<br/>completed
        Delink->>Queue: Publish<br/>delink.completed
        Queue-->>SMS: Send notification
        SMS->>SMS: Notify operator
        SMS-->>User: SMS confirmation
    else Delink Failed
        Delink->>DB: Update status<br/>failed<br/>+ error message
        Delink->>Queue: Publish<br/>delink.failed
    end

---

sequenceDiagram
    actor Operator as Telecom Operator
    participant SFTP as SFTP Server
    participant Reconcile as Reconciliation<br/>Service
    participant NIMC as NIMC API
    participant NIBSS as NIBSS API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Queue as RabbitMQ
    participant Notify as Notification<br/>Service
    participant SMS as SMS Gateway

    Note over Operator,SMS: SIM Reconciliation Detection Workflow

    Operator->>SFTP: Export SIM inventory<br/>(daily 02:00 UTC)
    SFTP-->>Operator: CSV file created

    Reconcile->>SFTP: Scheduled job triggers<br/>(02:15 UTC)
    Reconcile->>SFTP: Download SIM inventory
    SFTP-->>Reconcile: CSV data

    Reconcile->>Reconcile: Parse CSV<br/>Extract MSISDN, SIM serial, IMSI

    loop For each MSISDN in CSV
        Reconcile->>DB: Check current owner
        DB-->>Reconcile: Current subscriber

        alt MSISDN has recent owner
            Reconcile->>NIMC: Verify NIN linkage
            NIMC-->>Reconcile: NIN + name
            Reconcile->>Reconcile: Compare: current MSISDN<br/>vs previous owner

            alt Recycled SIM Detected
                Reconcile->>DB: Insert recycled_sims record
                DB-->>Reconcile: Record ID
                Reconcile->>DB: Insert nin_linkages
                DB-->>Reconcile: Linkage ID

                Reconcile->>NIBSS: Check for BVN linkage
                NIBSS-->>Reconcile: BVN data (if exists)

                alt BVN Found
                    Reconcile->>DB: Insert bvn_linkages
                    DB-->>Reconcile: BVN linkage ID
                end

                Reconcile->>Queue: Publish<br/>recycled_sim.detected
                Queue-->>Reconcile: ACK
            end
        end
    end

    Note over Reconcile: Once CSV processing complete

    Reconcile->>DB: Summarize results
    DB-->>Reconcile: Detection stats

    Queue->>Notify: Consume recycled_sim events
    Notify->>DB: Fetch notification templates
    DB-->>Notify: Template content

    loop For each detected SIM
        Notify->>SMS: Send notification<br/>to previous owner
        SMS->>SMS: Notify about<br/>account takeover risk
    end

    Notify->>Queue: Publish<br/>reconciliation.completed

    Queue->>Reconcile: Update job status
    Reconcile->>DB: Store reconciliation stats
    DB-->>Reconcile: OK

---

sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Admin User
    participant UI as Admin Dashboard
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Upload as File Upload<br/>Service
    participant Validate as Validation<br/>Service
    participant Queue as RabbitMQ
    participant Process as Batch<br/>Processor
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Notify as Notification<br/>Service

    Note over Admin,Notify: Bulk CSV Upload & Processing Workflow

    Admin->>UI: Select bulk CSV file<br/>(recycled SIMs)
    UI->>API: POST /bulk/upload<br/>multipart/form-data

    API->>Upload: Process file upload
    Upload->>Upload: Store temp file<br/>/tmp/upload_xxxxx.csv
    Upload->>Validate: Validate CSV schema
    Validate->>Validate: Check headers<br/>& data types

    alt Validation Passes
        Upload->>Queue: Publish bulk.upload.queued<br/>file_id, row_count
        Queue-->>Upload: ACK
        Upload-->>API: 202 Accepted
        API-->>UI: Job ID + status URL

        Note over Queue: Async processing begins

        Queue->>Process: Consume bulk upload job
        Process->>Upload: Download temp file
        Upload-->>Process: CSV stream

        loop Process each CSV row
            Process->>Validate: Validate row data
            alt Row Valid
                Process->>DB: Insert recycled_sims
                DB-->>Process: Record ID
                Process->>DB: Insert nin_linkages
                DB-->>Process: Linkage ID
                Process->>Queue: Publish<br/>recycled_sim.detected
            else Row Invalid
                Process->>Process: Log error
                Process->>DB: Store error record
            end
        end

        Process->>DB: Update bulk job status<br/>completed
        DB-->>Process: OK

        Note over Queue,Notify: Notifications for detected SIMs

        Queue->>Notify: Consume all queued events
        loop Generate notifications
            Notify->>DB: Fetch templates
            Notify->>DB: Insert notification records
            Notify->>API: Send SMS/Email
        end

        UI->>API: Poll /bulk/jobs/{id}<br/>for completion
        API->>DB: Get job status
        DB-->>API: Status + results
        API-->>UI: Display summary<br/>rows processed, errors, created records

    else Validation Fails
        Validate-->>Upload: Error details
        Upload-->>API: 400 Bad Request
        API-->>UI: Show error message<br/>& remediation steps
    end

---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User/Admin
    participant UI as Web Browser
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Cache as Redis Cache
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: API Authentication & Authorization Flow

    User->>UI: Enter credentials
    UI->>API: POST /auth/login<br/>username, password

    API->>Auth: Authenticate user
    Auth->>DB: Lookup user by username
    DB-->>Auth: User record + hashed pwd

    alt Password matches
        Auth->>Auth: Generate JWT token<br/>exp: 24h, sub: user_id
        Auth->>Auth: Embed claims:<br/>role, permissions, ip_address
        Auth->>Auth: Sign JWT with RS256<br/>(private key)
        Auth-->>API: JWT token
        API->>Cache: Store session<br/>key=user_id, val=token_data
        Cache-->>API: OK
        API-->>UI: 200 OK<br/>token, refresh_token, expires_in
        UI->>UI: Store token in<br/>localStorage
    else Password incorrect
        Auth-->>API: 401 Unauthorized
        API-->>UI: 401 Invalid credentials
    end

    Note over User,DB: Subsequent API Requests

    User->>UI: Request protected resource
    UI->>API: GET /reconciliation/sims<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWT}

    API->>Auth: Validate JWT signature
    Auth->>Auth: Verify RS256 signature
    alt Signature valid & token not expired
        Auth->>Auth: Extract claims
        Auth->>Cache: Check session<br/>exists & valid
        Cache-->>Auth: Session data
        alt Session valid
            Auth->>Auth: Check permissions<br/>for /reconciliation/sims
            alt User has read permission
                Auth-->>API: 200 OK<br/>decoded_claims
            else Insufficient permission
                Auth-->>API: 403 Forbidden
            end
        else Session invalidated
            Auth-->>API: 401 Unauthorized<br/>Session expired
        end
    else Invalid signature or expired
        Auth-->>API: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    alt Authorized
        API->>DB: Query SIM records
        DB-->>API: Results
        API-->>UI: 200 OK<br/>SIM data
    else Unauthorized
        API-->>UI: 401/403<br/>Error message
    end
